title: Putumayo World Music (2004)_All Albums
description:
Putumayo World Music is a New York City-based record label, specializing in compilations of music from various nations, regions or musical styles which may be classified as world music.

This torrent include all albums released in 2001 by Putumayo.


List of Albums:

Sahara Lounge (20 January 2004)
World Reggae (24 February 2004)
Sing Along with Putumayo (23 March 2004)
Women of Africa (27 April 2004)
Nuevo Latino (25 May 2004)
Greece: A Musical Odyssey (29 June 2004)
Caribbean Playground (27 July 2004)
World Groove (24 August 2004)
Women of Latin America (21 September 2004)
Blues Lounge (5 October 2004)
Music from the Chocolate Lands (9 November 2004)
South Pacific Islands (23 November 2004)


Format .mp3
Art .jpeg of CD covers included
